PN,31901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776345056
OL,3,C'Broken system' caused migrant
OL,4,CKebatu's accidental release, Lammy says
OL,6,FThe accidental prison release of
OL,7,Fmigrant sex offender Hadush Kebatu was
OL,8,Fcaused by a "broken system", Justice
OL,9,FSecretary David Lammy has told ITV
OL,10,FNews.
OL,12,FHe was speaking after an independent
OL,13,Finvestigation into mistaken prisoner
OL,14,Freleases, including that of Kebatu,
OL,15,Fwas released on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776345056
OL,3,C'Broken system' caused migrant
OL,4,CKebatu's accidental release, Lammy says
OL,6,FThe Independent Review into Releases
OL,7,Fin Error, led by Dame Lynne Owens,
OL,8,Ffound that overly complex processes,
OL,9,Fpoor communication between
OL,10,Fdepartments, and outdated technology
OL,11,Fare driving errors in the prison
OL,12,Frelease system, including wrongful
OL,13,Freleases.
OL,15,F"Dame Lynne has found that the system
OL,16,Fis broken," the deputy prime minister
OL,17,Ftold ITV News. "It's a product of
OL,18,Funderinvestment over successive
OL,19,Fgovernments, but particularly the last
OL,20,F14 years of austerity."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776345056
OL,3,C'Broken system' caused migrant
OL,4,CKebatu's accidental release, Lammy says
OL,6,FIn response, the deputy prime minister
OL,7,Fsaid the government would be investing
OL,8,F#50 million in a new prison release
OL,9,Fbiometric system, as well as better
OL,10,Fstaff training.
OL,12,FHe said the government will "do
OL,13,Feverything in our power" to restore
OL,14,Ftrust in the UK's prison system before
OL,15,Fthe end of the next parliament, adding
OL,16,Fthat it needs to become more digital
OL,17,Fand streamlined.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776345056
OL,3,C'Broken system' caused migrant
OL,4,CKebatu's accidental release, Lammy says
OL,6,FThe review found that there were
OL,7,F"missed opportunities" to prevent the
OL,8,Faccidental release of Kebatu in
OL,9,FOctober 2025.
OL,11,FThe Ethiopian national had been jailed
OL,12,Ffor a year in September for sexually
OL,13,Fassaulting a 14-year-old girl in
OL,14,FEpping, Essex.
OL,16,FHis accidental release from HMP
OL,17,FChelmsford sparked national outcry and
OL,18,Fled to a two-day police manhunt.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776345056
OL,3,C'Broken system' caused migrant
OL,4,CKebatu's accidental release, Lammy says
OL,6,FKebatu was eventually located and
OL,7,Farrested in London's Finsbury Park,
OL,8,Fhaving travelled there from
OL,9,FChelmsford. He was later deported to
OL,10,FEthiopia.
OL,12,FKebatu's release served as a catalyst
OL,13,Ffor increased scrutiny of the prison
OL,14,Frelease system.
OL,16,FOn Wednesday, figures released by the
OL,17,FMinistry of Justice showed 179
OL,18,Fprisoners were mistakenly released in
OL,19,Fthe space of one year, between April
OL,20,F2025 and March 2026.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776345056
OL,3,C'Broken system' caused migrant
OL,4,CKebatu's accidental release, Lammy says
OL,6,FAsked whether there had been any
OL,7,Fdisciplinary process for the officers
OL,8,Finvolved in the early release of
OL,9,FKebatu, Lammy said he did not wish to
OL,10,F"blame the frontline staff for what
OL,11,FDame Lynne finds is a broken system.
OL,13,F"It's a system error, and of course
OL,14,Fit's our job as government to get on
OL,15,Fand fix that," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776345056
OL,3,C'Broken system' caused migrant
OL,4,CKebatu's accidental release, Lammy says
OL,6,FDame Lynne's report found key problems
OL,7,Fin the prison release system,
OL,8,Fincluding overly complex sentencing
OL,9,Fcalculations, inconsistent recording
OL,10,Fpractices, and a heavy reliance on
OL,11,Fmanual data entry across outdated and
OL,12,Fdisconnected IT systems, as well as an
OL,13,Foveruse of paper-based systems.
OL,15,FAdditionally, poor coordination
OL,16,Fbetween courts and prisons has further
OL,17,Fincreased the risk of missing or
OL,18,Fincorrect information, while pressure
OL,19,Fon staff raises the likelihood of
OL,20,Fhuman error.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776345056
OL,3,C'Broken system' caused migrant
OL,4,CKebatu's accidental release, Lammy says
OL,6,FThe report recommended better
OL,7,Fdigitalisation and interconnectivity
OL,8,Fof systems across the criminal justice
OL,9,Fsystem, as well as more efficient
OL,10,Ftraining of staff.
OL,12,FThe deputy prime minister told ITV
OL,13,FNews the government will be accepting
OL,14,Fall of Dame Lynne's recommendations.
OL,16,F"We have to move to a digital system,"
OL,17,FLammy told ITV News' UK Editor Paul
OL,18,FBrand. "A system in which all staff
OL,19,Fcan follow the prisoner and know
OL,20,Fexactly the date the prisoner should
OL,21,Fbe released."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776345056
OL,3,C'Broken system' caused migrant
OL,4,CKebatu's accidental release, Lammy says
OL,6,FLammy said junior prison staff had
OL,7,Fbeen left having to wade through
OL,8,F"mountains of paper" to make
OL,9,Fcalculations about whether a prisoner
OL,10,Fshould be released.
OL,12,FHe added that he intends to make the
OL,13,Fchanges before the end of this
OL,14,Fparliament.
OL,16,FSpeaking to ITV News exclusively, the
OL,17,Ffather of Kebatu's then-14-year-old
OL,18,Fvictim said he had no confidence in
OL,19,Fthe government, saying: "The
OL,20,Fgovernment is to blame in my eyes."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776345056
OL,3,C'Broken system' caused migrant
OL,4,CKebatu's accidental release, Lammy says
OL,6,F"The government is half of the
OL,7,Fproblem, if not all of the problem,"
OL,8,Fhe said. "They had the power to shut
OL,9,Fthe hotel down, but they haven't," he
OL,10,Fadded, referencing the use of hotels
OL,11,Fused to house asylum seekers.
OL,13,FThe Bell Hotel, where Kebatu was
OL,14,Fliving before his conviction, became
OL,15,Fthe focal point of demonstrations and
OL,16,Fcounter-protests last summer following
OL,17,Fhis criminal charges.
OL,19,FThe victim's father at the time said
OL,20,FKebatu's accidental release caused his
OL,21,Fdaughter a lot of distress.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776345056
OL,3,C'Broken system' caused migrant
OL,4,CKebatu's accidental release, Lammy says
OL,6,FIn a statement, via her father, she
OL,7,Fsaid: "I think it's disgusting how me
OL,8,Fand my family have been treated in all
OL,9,Fof this and it's not fair that he was
OL,10,Freleased by accident. I feel like I
OL,11,Fwas put in danger all over again."
OL,13,FShe also described how she found out
OL,14,Fabout Kebatu's accidental release via
OL,15,Fsocial media, rather than through an
OL,16,Fofficial channel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776345056
OL,3,C'Broken system' caused migrant
OL,4,CKebatu's accidental release, Lammy says
OL,6,F"The way that the young victim of
OL,7,FKebatu and her family found out about
OL,8,Fthis was unacceptable. I apologise to
OL,9,Fthem, I apologise again," Lammy told
OL,10,FITV News on Wednesday.
OL,12,F"We cannot have a system where this
OL,13,Fhappens."
OL,15,FAsked whether it was right for Kebatu
OL,16,Fto have been removed from the country
OL,17,Fbefore he had served his full
OL,18,Fsentence, Lammy said it was, and that
OL,19,Fit was a "public policy decision."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776345056
OL,3,C'Broken system' caused migrant
OL,4,CKebatu's accidental release, Lammy says
OL,6,F"It is right that where you've got a
OL,7,Fforeign national offender in a high-
OL,8,Fprofile case that they are removed
OL,9,Fswiftly from the country at the end of
OL,10,Fthe statutory term with which their
OL,11,Fsentence is served.
OL,13,F"That should have happened in this
OL,14,Fcase and it's our duty to ensure that
OL,15,Fit happens properly over the course of
OL,16,Fthe next few years."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776345056
OL,3,C'Broken system' caused migrant
OL,4,CKebatu's accidental release, Lammy says
OL,6,FLammy said he wished to "bring an end
OL,7,Fto the public concern about releases
OL,8,Fin error", reaffirming that the
OL,9,Fgovernment would implement all of Dame
OL,10,FLynne's recommendations.
OL,12,FKebatu's victim's father told ITV News
OL,13,Fthat the review had given him
OL,14,F"reassurance", saying "I do hope these
OL,15,Frecommendations are put to parliament
OL,16,Fand that they're going to look into
OL,17,Fthis and prevent it happening to
OL,18,Fsomeone else's family."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
